  "detailed_description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>DEFEND YOUR BUBBLE!</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Inspired by classic arcade-style gameplay, defend all that is bubble-like from the pointy bad guys who want to pop you! Dash, shoot, and defend both yourself and your base from being popped by infinite onslaughts of thumbtacks, pencils, sewing needles, and more!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3640860/extras/68a5b81e7274b1864b81730a9ad9d8bb.poster.avif?t=1750959015\" width=400 height=210 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3640860/extras/68a5b81e7274b1864b81730a9ad9d8bb.webm?t=1750959015\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3640860/extras/68a5b81e7274b1864b81730a9ad9d8bb.mp4?t=1750959015\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>UPGRADE YOUR OFFENSE!</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >With<strong> 8 ways to upgrade you and your base bubble</strong>, alongside the help of<strong> 6 unique and game-changing super attacks</strong>, you're never going to feel fragile! As <strong>upgrades</strong> unlock throughout your run, you'll become gradually more powerful as enemies grow in number and strength. <strong>Supers</strong> appear randomly to shake up the pace of the waves, allowing for strategic and engaging runs all while mowing down hordes of enemies!</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>DON'T LET THEM POP YOUR BUBBLE!</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Featuring:</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >9 Enemies spread across 3 tiers of difficulty!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >8 Upgrades for you and your base!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >6 Game-changing super attacks!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Hordes, Bosses, and Themed Waves!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Stats, a tutorial, customization, and more!</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3640860/extras/6a05b8eb6abf246658e475cd972f2c5a.poster.avif?t=1750959015\" width=400 height=298 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3640860/extras/6a05b8eb6abf246658e475cd972f2c5a.webm?t=1750959015\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3640860/extras/6a05b8eb6abf246658e475cd972f2c5a.mp4?t=1750959015\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>(Note: no bubbles were harmed in the making of this clip.)</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>DEFEND YOUR BUBBLE!</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Inspired by classic arcade-style gameplay, defend all that is bubble-like from the pointy bad guys who want to pop you! Dash, shoot, and defend both yourself and your base from being popped by infinite onslaughts of thumbtacks, pencils, sewing needles, and more!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3640860/extras/68a5b81e7274b1864b81730a9ad9d8bb.poster.avif?t=1750959015\" width=400 height=210 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3640860/extras/68a5b81e7274b1864b81730a9ad9d8bb.webm?t=1750959015\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3640860/extras/68a5b81e7274b1864b81730a9ad9d8bb.mp4?t=1750959015\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>UPGRADE YOUR OFFENSE!</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >With<strong> 8 ways to upgrade you and your base bubble</strong>, alongside the help of<strong> 6 unique and game-changing super attacks</strong>, you're never going to feel fragile! As <strong>upgrades</strong> unlock throughout your run, you'll become gradually more powerful as enemies grow in number and strength. <strong>Supers</strong> appear randomly to shake up the pace of the waves, allowing for strategic and engaging runs all while mowing down hordes of enemies!</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>DON'T LET THEM POP YOUR BUBBLE!</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Featuring:</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >9 Enemies spread across 3 tiers of difficulty!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >8 Upgrades for you and your base!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >6 Game-changing super attacks!</p></li><li><p 